content: Is there a way or place to learn further information on a given JiraSpec warning (https://build.fhir.org/ig/HL7/cancer-reporting/qa.html) against a CI build? I'm wondering if the ToC and Artifact Index need to be listed as pages in JiraSpec. Or an extra whitespace lingering somewhere.
Whitespaces shouldn't matter. Have you done a diff on the two files it references in the warning?
Ah, it ended up being a recent change to the ballot URL (and a pesky lurking parentheses in a title); the warning should be resolved after the merge. Thanks
